'''萊斯特廣場奧迪安電影院'''（Odeon Leicester Square）是位於[[倫敦|倫敦]][[萊斯特廣場|萊斯特廣場]]的一座[[電影院|電影院]]，藍色霓虹燈是這座電影院的標誌。萊斯特廣場奧迪安電影院是倫敦最著名的電影院之一，也是許多影片在歐洲或世界的首映地<ref name="bfi131">page 131, Odeon Cinemas 1: Oscar Deutsch Entertains Our Nation, Allen Eyles, 2002, British Film Institute Publishing</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://cinematreasures.org/theater/841/ |title=Cinema Treasures - Odeon Leicester Square |accessdate=2009-11-16 |author=Steffan Laugharne, Ken Roe |work=Cinema Treasures |archive-date=2009-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201073447/http://cinematreasures.org/theater/841 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.mtv.co.uk/entertainment/harry-potter/gallery/245831-world-premiere-of-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-par Odeon Leicester Square: World Premiere of 'Harry Potter' And The Deathly Hallows Pt 1] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/entertainment/harry-potter/gallery/245831-world-premiere-of-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-par |date=20131014111257 }} ''[[MTV|MTV]]'' Retrieved 24 March 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturepicturegalleries/6787259/The-world-premiere-of-Avatar-at-Odeon-Leicester-Square.html The world premiere of Avatar at Odeon Leicester Square] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturepicturegalleries/6787259/The-world-premiere-of-Avatar-at-Odeon-Leicester-Square.html |date=20160810204413 }} ''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]]'' Retrieved 24 March 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/celebritynews/7320490/Alice-in-Wonderland-premiere-in-Leicester-Square-London.html Alice in Wonderland premiere in Leicester Square, London] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/celebritynews/7320490/Alice-in-Wonderland-premiere-in-Leicester-Square-London.html |date=20150925122450 }} ''The Telegraph'' Retrieved 24 March 2011</ref>，並且是皇家電影表演的舉辦地<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/5216256.stm Casino Royale is 60th royal film] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/5216256.stm |date=20090325063803 }} ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]'' Retrieved 24 March 2011</ref>。
